@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pkacxi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((v0 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.71)))
    v0 = 0.38
    tmp = v0
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.34) + 0.74) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.79 * v0 + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.50 * wp.sin(v0 + 0.08)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos((tmp + 0.46 * v1 + 0.07)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v1 + (v2 + 0.62 - tmp + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
